  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to GNOME Devel Docs</title>

    <para>
      The <application>GNOME Devel Docs</application> package contains documentation
      on a11y for developing the <application>GNOME</application> Desktop environment.
    </para>

    &lfs70_checked;

